text: Excess Baggage may refer to: *Checked baggage that exceeds a carrier's maximum permitted weight or volume and for which an additional charge is payable ==Films== *Excess Baggage (1928 film), American lost silent comedy *Excess Baggage (1933 film), British comedy *Excess Baggage (1997 film), American crime comedy Alicia Silverstone and Benicio del Toro ==Radio and television== *Excess Baggage (radio programme), 2010–12 British travel series on BBC Radio 4 *Excess Baggage (Australian TV series), 2012 Australian reality show
title: Excess Baggage
